00:52:18.457 --> 00:52:20.577
your organization, you mentioned
that you do not

00:52:20.577 --> 00:52:24.660
prefer having contracts
with your employees.

00:52:24.660 --> 00:52:27.000
And I'm wondering what that
means not to have contracts,

00:52:27.000 --> 00:52:29.890
and why do you do it?

00:52:29.890 --> 00:52:30.753
MAURICE ''HANK'' GREENBERG:
I didn't quite understand.

00:52:30.753 --> 00:52:33.780
PROFESSOR ROBERT SHILLER:
About your contracts.

00:52:33.780 --> 00:52:34.320
MAURICE ''HANK'' GREENBERG:
Yeah.

00:52:34.320 --> 00:52:39.990
I didn't think that you ought
to hold and have a contract,

00:52:39.990 --> 00:52:41.660
that you stay if you weren't
doing the job.

00:52:44.270 --> 00:52:45.610
But you have to start
someplace and it

00:52:45.610 --> 00:52:46.460
started with me.

